Maybe she should have gone on a tell spree, ranting about how Fuvi didn't think she deserved what she had gotten, gathered support for herself and vilified me for claiming otherwise.  Of course she would only invest energy in something that couldn't possibly be fun for her and would result in her enjoying a game that much less, so she did what I consider the right thing.<br>
<br>
I've never stopped having fun Kurley, in fact this post is a lot of fun, pointing out the self-destructive behavior of someone who made so much effort to pull me down brings a smile to my face, because indeed I am an @sshole and a happy one at that. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uheagan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Heagan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>One Feisty Dwarf!</span><br>  Posts: 564<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/26/02 6:10:05 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hihi</span><hr size=1> Mod edit: Personal attacks like this are not acceptable here.<br>
